<p class="h">
<b>The measure of value, medium of exchange, a store of value</b>
</p>

<p>
<b>Money</b> is a MEASURE, which is the universal equivalent of value of goods and services. Functions of money: 
<br/>
- The measure of value;
<br/>
- The medium of exchange;
<br/>
- <i>Storage means (controversial statement)</i>.
